 \"异常指标包括 node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes (从 9412222976.0 减少到 5883379712.0) 和 node_memory_usage_rate (从 42.49 增加到 63.53)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"节点内存可用量显著减少，内存使用率显著增加\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常指标包括 node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes (从 7431983104.0 增加到 11243573248.0)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"节点内存可用量显著增加\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常指标包括 pod_cpu_usage (从 0.0 增加到 0.0)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage 未变化，但需关注其是否与其他指标关联\"\n    }\n  ]\n}", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的链路追踪数据，我现在进行全面的异常分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"DNS解析失败：connection error: desc = 'transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving'，出现213次错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation调用延迟从正常24.5ms激增至1739ms（70倍增长），异常发生30次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService/PlaceOrder调用延迟从正常148-156ms激增至1.8-2.0秒（10-13倍增长），影响所有frontend实例\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice内部调用\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService/Charge延迟从13.8ms增至50.6ms（3.6倍），ShippingService/GetQuote从9.4ms增至72.4ms（7.7倍），CartService/GetCart从8.1ms增至123.3ms（15倍）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n**主要异常模式**：\n1. **EmailService DNS解析失败**：这是最严重的错误，导致checkoutservice无法连接到emailservice\n2